data.description: Sit in your back yard and enjoy the peace and quiet .Take the short walk to the lake and catch a few fish.This spacious home is ready for you. 5 Bedrooms. 3 and a half Baths. Large Primary bedroom with Fireplace and large bath with separate Jacuzzi tub and shower. Split bedroom plan with bedroom and bonus upstairs. Has eat in kitched with lots of cabinets Tons of counter space and granite counter tops. 3 car side entry garage plus storage room.Hardwood floors throughout living areas Carpet in bedrooms. Has a backup generator for those power outages. Lots more features call to set up your private viewing.    Assumable loan at 5.625 interest rate
